Name: trust-dns-resolver
License File: LICENSE-APACHE, LICENSE-MIT
Description:

trust-dns-resolver is used in the Fuchsia DNS resolver and is what handles the
actual DNS part.

This is trust-dns-resolver 0.22.0 from September 2022. This fork exists to allow
us to implement additional functionality without needing to first upgrade the
package. It has changed a lot in the meantime, especially its
dependencies. Everything we do here will be proposed upstream for when we do
eventually upgrade.

This fork can be removed once upstream has equivalent functionality to
b/492137263 (will be filled in more once patch is sent for review upstream).